quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  5,83,aur jab is ( kitaab ) ko suntay hain jo ( sab se pehlay ) paighambar ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) par nazil hui to tum dekhte ho ke un ki aankhon se ansoo jari ho jatay hain is liye ke unhon ne haq baat pehchan li aur woh ( khuda ki janab mein ) arz karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum imaan le aeye to hum ko maan-ne walon mein likh le
  5,84,aur hameinkiya howa hai ke khuda par aur haq baat par jo hamaray paas aayi hai imaan nah layein aur hum umeed rakhtay hain ke perwar-digaar hum ko naik bundon ke sath ( bahisht mein ) daakhil kere ga
  5,85,to khuda ne un ko is kehnay ke aiwz ( bahisht ke ) baagh ataa farmaiye jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain woh hamesha un mein rahen ge aur naiko karon ka yahi sila hai
  5,86,aur jin logon ne kufarkiya aur hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya woh jahanumi hain
  5,87,momino! jo pakeeza cheezein khuda ne tumahray liye halal ki hain un ko haraam nah karo aur hadd se nah badho ke khuda hadd se bherne walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  5,88,aur jo halal tayyab rozi khuda ne tum ko di hai usay khao aur khuda se jis par imaan rakhtay ho drtay raho
  5,89,khuda tumhari be iradah qasmon par tum se muwakhza nahi kere ga lekin pukhta qasmon par ( jin ke khilaaf karo ge ) muwakhza kere ga to is ka kaffara das mohtajon ko ost darjay ka khana khilana hai jo tum apne ahal vayal ko khelati ho ya un ko kapray dena ya aik ghulam azad karna aur jis ko muyassar nah ho woh teen rozay rakhay yeh tumhari qasmon ka kaffara hai jab tum qasam kha lo ( aur usay toar do ) aur ( tum ko ) chahiye ke apni qasmon ki hifazat karo is terhan khuda tumahray ( samjhane ke ) liye apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay tum shukar karo
